trans-unit.source: Represents an attribute declaration.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en attributtet-deklarering.

trans-unit.source: A CodeAttributeDeclaration can be used to represent an expression that declares an attribute.
trans-unit.target: En CodeAttributeDeclaration kan brukes til å representere et uttrykk som deklarerer et attributt.

trans-unit.source: The attribute name and the arguments for the attribute are stored as properties of the object.
trans-unit.target: Attributtnavnet og argumentene for attributtet er lagret som egenskapene for objektet.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeArgument> can be used to represent each argument for the attribute.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeArgument>kan brukes til å representere hver argumentet for attributtet.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeArgument>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration"></xref> class using the specified code type reference.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av den angitte koden referansetypen.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeType` parameter is used to set the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration.AttributeType%2A> and <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration.Name%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Den `attributeType` parameteren brukes til å angi den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration.AttributeType%2A>og <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration.Name%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration.Name%2A> </xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration.AttributeType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"></xref> that identifies the attribute.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"> </xref> som identifiserer attributtet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration"></xref> class using the specified name.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av det angitte navnet.

trans-unit.source: The name of the attribute.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på attributtet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration"></xref> class using the specified code type reference and arguments.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av den angitte koden referansetypen og argumenter.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeType` parameter is used to set the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration.AttributeType%2A> and <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration.Name%2A> properties, and the `arguments` parameter is used to set the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration.Arguments%2A> property for the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration>.
trans-unit.target: Den `attributeType` parameteren brukes til å angi den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration.AttributeType%2A>og <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration.Name%2A>Egenskaper og `arguments` parameteren brukes til å angi <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration.Arguments%2A>egenskapen for <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration>.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration> </xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration.Arguments%2A> </xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration.Name%2A> </xref:System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration.AttributeType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"></xref> that identifies the attribute.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"> </xref> som identifiserer attributtet.

trans-unit.source: An array of type <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeArgument"></xref> that contains the arguments for the attribute.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av typen <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeArgument"> </xref> som inneholder argumentene for attributtet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration"></xref> class using the specified name and arguments.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av angitt navn og argumenter.

trans-unit.source: The name of the attribute.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på attributtet.

trans-unit.source: An array of type <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeArgument"></xref> that contains the arguments for the attribute.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av typen <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeArgument"> </xref> som inneholder argumentene for attributtet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the arguments for the attribute.
trans-unit.target: Henter argumentene for attributtet.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeArgumentCollection"></xref> that contains the arguments for the attribute.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeArgumentCollection"> </xref> som inneholder argumentene for attributtet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the code type reference for the code attribute declaration.
trans-unit.target: Henter referansetypen kode for deklarasjon av code-attributtet.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"></xref> that identifies the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"> </xref> som identifiserer den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclaration"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the attribute being declared.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir navnet på attributtet som er deklarert.

trans-unit.source: The name of the attribute.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på attributtet.
